  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/48712e756deba7009450cce148d10e0a.poster.avif?t=1767499148\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/48712e756deba7009450cce148d10e0a.webm?t=1767499148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/48712e756deba7009450cce148d10e0a.mp4?t=1767499148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/5b988defca74e53c3c8cfe4ebdac062e.poster.avif?t=1767499148\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/5b988defca74e53c3c8cfe4ebdac062e.webm?t=1767499148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/5b988defca74e53c3c8cfe4ebdac062e.mp4?t=1767499148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dear Players,</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Dunkenwood House—your new school.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Arenda Finch. After being expelled from your church-run girls’ school for speaking too many blasphemous words, you have been transferred here. To adjust to your new life, it helps to remember a few rules:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are not a detective.</strong><br>Your task is simply to study, repair your relationship with your brother, graduate, and inherit the fortune left to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But this manor has a long and intricate history. Strange things happen here, and strange people live here. Conspiracies, crimes, and malevolent individuals may well exist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will face choices—some that save you from immediate danger, and others that shape the person you become.<br>If life at school grows dull, you may look further into the house’s past, your family’s secrets, and the darkness surrounding those you meet.<br>But the truth never comes without a price.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck.<br>Your new life begins here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Our Discord community :</strong></i></u>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/d54eb83b62dcf8bcfacd01096305723f.poster.avif?t=1767499148\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/d54eb83b62dcf8bcfacd01096305723f.webm?t=1767499148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/d54eb83b62dcf8bcfacd01096305723f.mp4?t=1767499148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Demon’s Game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is not a detective story.<br>There are conspiracies, crimes, and those who wish you harm.<br>But when the inhuman intervenes, do not attempt to understand it through human logic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Choice Between Life and Death</strong><br>Some decisions alter your immediate circumstances.<br>Others shape your future.<br>All of them matter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Forbidden Love</strong><br>To love someone you should not.<br>To protect the people you care for, or sacrifice them for something greater.<br>If they truly love you, shouldn't they be willing to give everything—even their lives?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And then—</strong><br>???<br>Uncover the concealed truths behind the main narrative and the unspoken secrets of the others around you.<br>But truth demands payment.<br>You may have to die more than once.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/001976e8d03a52fe4ab05cad527071fb.poster.avif?t=1767499148\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/001976e8d03a52fe4ab05cad527071fb.webm?t=1767499148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/001976e8d03a52fe4ab05cad527071fb.mp4?t=1767499148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/48712e756deba7009450cce148d10e0a.poster.avif?t=1767499148\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/48712e756deba7009450cce148d10e0a.webm?t=1767499148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/48712e756deba7009450cce148d10e0a.mp4?t=1767499148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/5b988defca74e53c3c8cfe4ebdac062e.poster.avif?t=1767499148\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/5b988defca74e53c3c8cfe4ebdac062e.webm?t=1767499148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965680/extras/5b988defca74e53c3c8cfe4ebdac062e.mp4?t=1767499148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dear Players,</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Dunkenwood House—your new school.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Arenda Finch. After being expelled from your church-run girls’ school for speaking too many blasphemous words, you have been transferred here. To adjust to your new life, it helps to remember a few rules:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are not a detective.</strong><br>Your task is simply to study, repair your relationship with your brother, graduate, and inherit the fortune left to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But this manor has a long and intricate history. Strange things happen here, 